F00:0051       ;
F00:0052       ; objet: 
F00:0053       ;	- nb points
F00:0054       ;	- ( N° de point * 16 ) * N
F00:0055       ;	- pointeur vers points variables ( morceau de l'objet animé )
F00:0056       ;
F00:0057       ; animation : 
F00:0058       ;	  - nombre d'objets de la scene
F00:0059       ;     - pointeur vers objet
F00:0060       ;     - X,Y,Z objet
F00:0061       ;     - increment X, increment Y , increment Z
F00:0062       ;     - increment angle X, increment angle Y , increment angle Z
F00:0063       ;	  - angles depart X,Y,Z
F00:0064       ;	  - nb frames rotation classique
F00:0065       ;	  - objet de destination d'une transformation, 0 = pas de transformation
F00:0066       ;	  - nombre étapes transformation, 0 = pas de transformation
F00:0067       ;     - pointeur vers data animation, 0 = pas d'anim
F00:0068       ;     - nombre d'étapes en frame, 0 = pas d'anim
F00:0069       ;	  - zoom / position observateur en Z
F00:0070       
F00:0071       ;		appeller calc3D en ayant rempli
F00:0072       ;			- pointeur_points_objet_en_cours
F00:0073       ;			- nb_points_objet_en_cours
F00:0074       ;			- pointeur_buffer_destination_calculs
F00:0075       
F00:0076       ; transformation
F00:0077       ;	objet source
F00:0078       ; 	objet destination
F00:0079       ;	nombre d'étapes = nb etapes rotation
F00:0080       ;	pour chaque point, (X destination - X Source) / nombre d'étapes = pas en X
F00:0081       ;   idem Y et Z , calculer le pas en Y et Z 
F00:0082       ;	* 2^15
F00:0083       ;	table increments_pas_transformations : 3 * 4 *64
F00:0084       ;
F00:0085       
F00:0086       ; animation:
F00:0087       ;  calcul normal de l'objet
F00:0088       ; deuxieme boucle pour la partie animée ?
F00:0089       ;	- pointeur vers coordonnées des points en cours ( actualisé à chaque frame)

F00:0586       ;----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
F00:0587       RM_init:
F00:0588       ; ne fait que verifier la version de Risc OS...
F00:0589       	str		lr,save_lr
               S01:000082A4:  20 E0 8F E5
F00:0590       ; get OS version
F00:0591       	MOV     R0,#129
               S01:000082A8:  81 00 A0 E3
F00:0592       	MOV     R1,#0
               S01:000082AC:  00 10 A0 E3
F00:0593       	MOV     R2,#0xFF
               S01:000082B0:  FF 20 A0 E3
F00:0594       	SWI     OS_Byte
               S01:000082B4:  06 00 00 EF
F00:0595       
F00:0596       	STRB    R1,os_version
               S01:000082B8:  48 15 CF E5
F00:0597       
F00:0598       ; Risc os 3.5 ? => sortie
F00:0599       	CMP     R1,#0xA5
               S01:000082BC:  A5 00 51 E3
F00:0600       	beq		exit
               S01:000082C0:  C5 FF FF 0A
F00:0601       	
F00:0602       	ldr		lr,save_lr
               S01:000082C4:  00 E0 9F E5
F00:0603       	mov		pc,lr
               S01:000082C8:  0E F0 A0 E1
F00:0604       save_lr:		.long		0
               S01:000082CC:  00 00 00 00
F00:0605       
F00:0606       ; SH decoded IRQ and FIQ masks
F00:0607       ;
F00:0608       ; to load/set/store IRQ and FIQ masks use:
F00:0609       ;
F00:0610       ; Rx=mask
F00:0611       ; Ry=&3200000 (IOC base)
F00:0612       ;
F00:0613       ;
F00:0614       ; LDRB Rx,[Ry,#&18+0]      ;load irqa mask (+0)
F00:0615       ; STRB Rx,oldirqa          ;store original mask
F00:0616       ; MOV  Rx,#%00100000       ;only allow timer 0 interrupt
F00:0617       ; STRB Rx,[Ry,#&18+2]      ;(note +2 on storing)
F00:0618       ;
F00:0619       ; LDRB Rx,[Ry,#&28+0]      ;load irqb mask (+0)
F00:0620       ; STRB Rx,oldirqb          ;store original mask
F00:0621       ; MOV  Rx,#%00000010       ;only allow sound interrupt
F00:0622       ; STRB Rx,[Ry,#&28+2]      ;(note +2 on storing)
F00:0623       ;
F00:0624       ;
F00:0625       
F00:0626       ;irqa mask = IOC (&3200000) + &18
F00:0627       ;
F00:0628       ;bit 0   - il6 0 printer busy / printer irq
F00:0629       ;    1   - il7 0 serial port ringing / low battery
F00:0630       ;    2   - if  0 printer ack / floppy index
F00:0631       ;    3s  - ir  1 vsync
F00:0632       ;    4   - por 0 power on
F00:0633       ;    5c  - tm0 0 timer 0
F00:0634       ;    6   - tm1 1 timer 1
F00:0635       ;    7   - 1   0 n/c      (fiq downgrade?)
F00:0636       ;
F00:0637       ;irqb mask = IOC (&3200000) + &28
F00:0638       ;
F00:0639       ;bit 0   - il0 0 expansion card fiq downgrade
F00:0640       ;    1   - il1 0 sound system buffer change
F00:0641       ;    2   - il2 0 serial port controller
F00:0642       ;    3   - il3 0 hdd controller / ide controller
F00:0643       ;    4   - il4 0 floppy changed / floppy interrupt
F00:0644       ;    5   - il5 0 expansion card interrupt
F00:0645       ;    6   - stx 1 keyboard transmit empty
F00:0646       ;    7cs - str 1 keyboard recieve full
F00:0647       ;
F00:0648       ; c = cmdline critical
F00:0649       ; s = desktop critical
F00:0650       ;
F00:0651       ;fiq mask (none are critical) = IOC (&3200000) + &38
F00:0652       ;
F00:0653       ;bit 0  - fh0 0 floppy data request / floppy dma
F00:0654       ;    1  - fh1 0 fdc interrupt / fh1 pin on ioc
F00:0655       ;    2  - fl  0 econet interrupt
F00:0656       ;    3  - c3  0 c3 on ioc
F00:0657       ;    4  - c4  0 c4 on ioc / serial interrupt (also IRQB bit2)
F00:0658       ;    5  - c5  0 c5 on ioc
F00:0659       ;    6  - il0 0 expansion card interrupt
F00:0660       ;    7  - 1   0 force fiq (always 1)
F00:0661       ;
F00:0662       ;cr
F00:0663       ;
F00:0664       ;bit 0 - c0 IIC data
F00:0665       ;    1 - c1 IIC clock
F00:0666       ;    2 - c2 floppy ready / density
F00:0667       ;    3 - c3 reset enable / unique id
F00:0668       ;    4 - c4 aux i/o connector / serial fiq
F00:0669       ;    5 - c5 speaker
F00:0670       ;    6 - if printer ack or floppy index
F00:0671       ;    7 - ir vsync
F00:0672       ;	
F00:0673       ;----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
F00:0674       RM_start:
F00:0675       	str		lr,save_lr
               S01:000082D0:  0C E0 0F E5
F00:0676       ; appel XOS car si appel OS_SWI si erreur, ça sort directement
F00:0677       	MOV		R0,#0x0C           ;claim FIQ
               S01:000082D4:  0C 00 A0 E3
F00:0678       	SWI		XOS_ServiceCall
               S01:000082D8:  30 00 02 EF
F00:0679       	bvs		exit
               S01:000082DC:  BE FF FF 6A
F00:0680       
F00:0681       
F00:0682       ; we own FIQs
F00:0683       
F00:0684       
F00:0685       	TEQP	PC,#0xC000001					; bit 27 & 26 = 1, bit 0=1 : IRQ Disable+FIRQ Disable+FIRQ mode ( pour récupérer et sauvegarde
               S01:000082E0:  43 F3 3F E3
F00:0686       ;	TEQP	PC,#0b11<<26 OR 0b01			;disable IRQs and FIQs, change to FIQ mode
F00:0687       	MOV		R0,R0
               S01:000082E4:  00 00 A0 E1
F00:0688       
F00:0689       	ADR       R0,fiqoriginal				; sauvegarde de R8-R14
               S01:000082E8:  05 0C 8F E2 1C 00 80 E2
F00:0690       	STMIA     R0,{R8-R14}
               S01:000082F0:  00 7F 80 E8
F00:0691       
F00:0692       	MOV       R1,#0x3200000
               S01:000082F4:  32 16 A0 E3
F00:0693       	LDRB      R0,[R1,#0x18]					; lecture et sauvegarde mask IRQ A
               S01:000082F8:  18 00 D1 E5
F00:0694       	STR       R0,oldIRQa
               S01:000082FC:  24 05 8F E5
F00:0695       	LDRB      R0,[R1,#0x28]					; lecture et sauvegarde mask IRQ B
               S01:00008300:  28 00 D1 E5
F00:0696       	STR       R0,oldIRQb
               S01:00008304:  20 05 8F E5
F00:0697       
F00:0698       ; When installing, we will start on the next VSync, so set IRQ for VSync only
F00:0699       ; and set T1 to contain 'vsyncvalue', so everything in place for VSync int...
F00:0700       
F00:0701       	MOV       R0,#0b00001000
               S01:00008308:  08 00 A0 E3
F00:0702       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x18+2]    ;set IRQA mask to %00001000 = VSync only : bit 3 sur mask IRQ A = vsync
               S01:0000830C:  1A 00 C1 E5
F00:0703       	MOV       R0,#0
               S01:00008310:  00 00 A0 E3
F00:0704       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x28+2]    ;set IRQB mask to 0					:	IRQ B mask à 0 = disabled
               S01:00008314:  2A 00 C1 E5
F00:0705       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x38+2]    ;set FIQ mask to 0 (disable FIQs)		:	FIRQ  mask à 0 = disabled
               S01:00008318:  3A 00 C1 E5
F00:0706       
F00:0707       ; Timer 1 / IRQ A
F00:0708       	MOV       R0,#0xFF           ;*v0.14* set max T1 - ensure T1 doesn't trigger before first VSync!
               S01:0000831C:  FF 00 A0 E3
F00:0709       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x50+2]    ;T1 low byte, +2 for write			: verrou / compteur = 0xFFFF
               S01:00008320:  52 00 C1 E5
F00:0710       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x54+2]    ;T1 high byte, +2 for write
               S01:00008324:  56 00 C1 E5
F00:0711       	STRB      R1,[R1,#0x58+2]    ;T1_go = reset T1					: remet le compteur a la valeur latch ( verrou)
               S01:00008328:  5A 10 C1 E5
F00:0712       
F00:0713       ; on prépare le compteur du Timer 1 qui tournera entre le Vsync et la 1ere ligne de hsync
F00:0714       	MOV       R0,#vsyncreturn_low_ligne199			;or ldr r8,vsyncval  - will reload with this on VSync...			
               S01:0000832C:  75 00 A0 E3
F00:0715       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x50+2]    				;T1 low byte, +2 for write									: verrou / compteur 
               S01:00008330:  52 00 C1 E5
F00:0716       	MOV       R0,#vsyncreturn_high_ligne199			;or mov r8,r8,lsr#8
               S01:00008334:  7E 00 A0 E3
F00:0717       	STRB      R0,[R1,#0x54+2]   					;T1 high byte, +2 for write								: verrou / compteur 
               S01:00008338:  56 00 C1 E5
F00:0718       
F00:0719       
F00:0720       ; poke our IRQ/FIQ code into &1C-&FC : copie des routines IRQ/FIRQ dans la mémoire basse en 0x18
F00:0721       	MOV       R0,#0
               S01:0000833C:  00 00 A0 E3
F00:0722       	LDR       R1,[R0,#0x18]      ;load current IRQ vector
               S01:00008340:  18 10 90 E5
F00:0723       	STR       R1,oldIRQbranch
               S01:00008344:  E8 14 8F E5
F00:0724       
F00:0725       	BIC       R1,R1,#0xFF000000
               S01:00008348:  FF 14 C1 E3
F00:0726       	MOV       R1,R1,LSL#2
               S01:0000834C:  01 11 A0 E1
F00:0727       	ADD       R1,R1,#0x18+8
               S01:00008350:  20 10 81 E2
F00:0728       	STR       R1,oldIRQaddress
               S01:00008354:  DC 14 8F E5
F00:0729

F00:0731       	ldr			R0,pointeur_fiqbase
               S01:00008358:  E0 04 9F E5
F00:0732       	MOV       R1,#0x18	
               S01:0000835C:  18 10 A0 E3
F00:0733       	LDMIA     R0!,{R2-R12}
               S01:00008360:  FC 1F B0 E8

               S01:00008368:  FC 1F B0 E8
F00:0736       	STMIA     R1!,{R2-R12}      ;22 pokey codey
               S01:0000836C:  FC 1F A1 E8

               S01:00008370:  FC 1F B0 E8
F00:0738       	STMIA     R1!,{R2-R12}      ;33 pokey codey
               S01:00008374:  FC 1F A1 E8

               S01:00008378:  FC 1F B0 E8

               S01:0000838C:  1C 00 A1 E8
F00:0745       
F00:0746       ; init des registres permanents

               S01:00008390:  32 E6 A0 E3
F00:0748       	mov			R12,#0x3400000
               S01:00008394:  0D C5 A0 E3
F00:0749       
F00:0750       
F00:0751       .equ 	FIQ_notHSync_valeur, 0xC0
F00:0752       ; on écrit l'adresse de la routine Vsync dans le code IRQ/FIRQ en bas de mémoire  pour revenir si vsync ou keyboard
F00:0753       	adr		R0,notHSync					;FNlong_adr("",0,notHSync)   ;set up VSync code after copying
               S01:00008398:  F0 00 8F E2

               S01:0000839C:  C0 10 A0 E3
F00:0755       	STR       R0,[R1]
               S01:000083A0:  00 00 81 E5
F00:0756       
F00:0757       ; sauvegarde de la première instruction pour vérifier la présence du code , pour ne pas lancer plusieurs fois RM, inu
F00:0758       ;	MOV       R0,#0
F00:0759       ;	LDR       R1,[R0,#0x18]      ;first IRQ instruction from our code
F00:0760       ;	STR       R1,newIRQfirstinst
F00:0761       
F00:0762       ; sortie
F00:0763       ;									mode SVC Supervisor
F00:0764       	TEQP      PC,#0b11				; %00<<26 OR %11;enable IRQs and FIQs, change to user mode
               S01:000083A4:  03 F0 3F E3
F00:0765       	MOV       R0,R0
               S01:000083A8:  00 00 A0 E1
F00:0766

               S01:000083AC:  E8 E0 1F E5
F00:0768       	mov		pc,lr					;exit in USER mode and with IRQs and FIQs on
               S01:000083B0:  0E F0 A0 E1
F00:0769       
F00:0770

F00:0772       RM_release:
F00:0773       	str		lr,save_lr
               S01:000083B4:  F0 E0 0F E5
F00:0774       
F00:0775       ; we own FIQs
F00:0776       				  
F00:0777       	TEQP      PC,#0x0C000001					; %11<<26 OR %01            ;disable IRQs and FIQs, switch FIQ mode
               S01:000083B8:  43 F3 3F E3
F00:0778       	MOV       R0,R0
               S01:000083BC:  00 00 A0 E1
F00:0779       
F00:0780       	MOV       R0,#0
               S01:000083C0:  00 00 A0 E3

               S01:000083C4:  68 14 9F E5
F00:0782       	STR       R1,[R0,#0x18]        ;restore original IRQ controller
               S01:000083C8:  18 10 80 E5
F00:0783       	
F00:0784       	MOV       R0,#0
               S01:000083CC:  00 00 A0 E3
F00:0785       	MOV       R1,#0x3200000
               S01:000083D0:  32 16 A0 E3

               S01:000083D4:  3A 00 C1 E5

F00:0792

F00:0799

               S01:000083F8:  34 E1 1F E5

               S01:000083FC:  0E F0 A0 E1
F00:0802

F00:1453       
F00:1454       ;--------------------------------------------------------------------
F00:1455       ;    Transformation
F00:1456       ;--------------------------------------------------------------------
F00:1457       
F00:1458       ;- dans la boucle d'initialisation des animations :
F00:1459       ;
F00:1460       ;	- calculer deltaX/nb etapes, delta Y / nb etapes, delta Z/nb etapes
F00:1461       ;	- multiplier chaque valeur par 2^15
F00:1462       ;	- stocker dans table_increments_pas_transformations : X source ,increment X, Y source, increment Y, Z source, incremen
F00:1463       ;			pointeur_table_increments_pas_transformations
F00:1464       ; fonction : preparation_transformation:
F00:1465       ;
F00:1466       ;
F00:1467       ;- dans la boucle de calcul des rotations/projections
F00:1468       ;	- remplir pointeur_buffer_coordonnees_objet_transformees:
F00:1469       ;		- avec calcul de table_increments_pas_transformations  : X + inc X, Y+inc Y , Z+inc Z, 
F00:1470       ;		- stocker le resultat dans table_increments_pas_transformations +0 +8 + 16
F00:1471       ;		- stocker le resultat / 2^15 dans pointeur_buffer_coordonnees_objet_transformees
F00:1472       
F00:1473       
F00:1474       preparation_transformation:
F00:1475       
F00:1476       
F00:1477       
F00:1478       		ldr		R12,pointeur_table_increments_pas_transformations						; destination pour les X Y Z et increments
               S01:00008E0C:  90 C8 9F E5
F00:1479       		ldr		R11,pointeur_coordonnees_objet_source_transformation					; points de l'objet source : X Y Z n°sprite
               S01:00008E10:  64 B8 9F E5
F00:1480       		ldr		R10,pointeur_coordonnees_objet_destination_transformation				; coordonnees objet destination : X Y Z n°sprite
               S01:00008E14:  64 A8 9F E5
F00:1481       		
F00:1482       		ldr		R9,nb_etapes_transformation
               S01:00008E18:  6C 98 9F E5
F00:1483       		
F00:1484       		ldr		R0,nb_points_objet_en_cours
               S01:00008E1C:  24 08 9F E5
F00:1485       		
F00:1486       boucle_preparation_transformation:
F00:1487       		
F00:1488       		mov		R7,#3
               S01:00008E20:  03 70 A0 E3
F00:1489       		
F00:1490       boucle_preparation_transformation_1_valeur:
F00:1491       
F00:1492       		ldr		R1,[R11],#4					; on recupere X point objet source
               S01:00008E24:  04 10 9B E4
F00:1493       		ldr		R2,[R10],#4					; on recupere X point objet destination
               S01:00008E28:  04 20 9A E4
F00:1494       		
F00:1495       		subs	R3,R2,R1					; Delta X = X destination - X source
               S01:00008E2C:  01 30 52 E0
F00:1496       
F00:1497       ; calcul du pas : il faut diviser R3 par R9
F00:1498       ; en tenant compte de R3 négatif ?
F00:1499       
F00:1500       ; si r3 négatif :
F00:1501        	mov R4,#0
               S01:00008E30:  00 40 A0 E3
F00:1502       	
F00:1503       
F00:1504       	cmp r3,#0
               S01:00008E34:  00 00 53 E3
F00:1505       	bpl .deltaX_positif
               S01:00008E38:  01 00 00 5A
F00:1506       ; r11 négatif
F00:1507       
F00:1508       	rsb r3,r3,#0
               S01:00008E3C:  00 30 63 E2
F00:1509       	mov r4,#1		; R5 = 1 si X negatif
               S01:00008E40:  01 40 A0 E3
F00:1510       
F00:1511       .deltaX_positif:
F00:1512       	mov		R3,R3,asl #15				; * 2^15
               S01:00008E44:  83 37 A0 E1
F00:1513       
F00:1514       ; R5 = ( R3 / R9 )
F00:1515       ; registres dispos	:  R5 R6 R7 R8 R13 R14
F00:1516       
F00:1517       	MOV      R5,#0     ;clear R5 to accumulate result
               S01:00008E48:  00 50 A0 E3
F00:1518       	MOV      R6,#1     ;set bit 0 in R6, which will be
               S01:00008E4C:  01 60 A0 E3
F00:1519       					   ;shifted left then right
F00:1520       .startdivX_transformation1:
F00:1521       	CMP      R9,R3
               S01:00008E50:  03 00 59 E1
F00:1522       	MOVLS    R9,R9,LSL#1
               S01:00008E54:  89 90 A0 91
F00:1523       	MOVLS    R6,R6,LSL#1
               S01:00008E58:  86 60 A0 91
F00:1524       	BLS      .startdivX_transformation1
               S01:00008E5C:  FB FF FF 9A
F00:1525       
F00:1526       .nextdivX_transformation1:
F00:1527       	CMP       R3,R9
               S01:00008E60:  09 00 53 E1
F00:1528       	SUBCS     R3,R3,R9
               S01:00008E64:  09 30 43 20
F00:1529       	ADDCS     R5,R5,R6
               S01:00008E68:  06 50 85 20
F00:1530       	MOVS      R6,R6,LSR#1
               S01:00008E6C:  A6 60 B0 E1
F00:1531       	MOVCC     R9,R9,LSR#1
               S01:00008E70:  A9 90 A0 31
F00:1532       	BCC			.nextdivX_transformation1
               S01:00008E74:  F9 FF FF 3A
F00:1533       
F00:1534       	cmp		R4,#0			; R3 était négatif ?
               S01:00008E78:  00 00 54 E3
F00:1535       	beq		.X_transformation_negatif
               S01:00008E7C:  00 00 00 0A
F00:1536       	rsb		r5,r5,#0		; alors résultat négatif
               S01:00008E80:  00 50 65 E2
F00:1537       	
F00:1538       .X_transformation_negatif:
F00:1539       
F00:1540       ; R5 = R3/R9
F00:1541       
F00:1542       	mov		R1,R1,asl #15	; X * 2^15
               S01:00008E84:  81 17 A0 E1
F00:1543       	
F00:1544       	str		R1,[R12],#4		; on stocke X * 2^15
               S01:00008E88:  04 10 8C E4
F00:1545       	str		R5,[R12],#4		; increment X * 2^15
               S01:00008E8C:  04 50 8C E4
F00:1546       	
F00:1547       	subs	R7,R7,#1
               S01:00008E90:  01 70 57 E2
F00:1548       	bgt		boucle_preparation_transformation_1_valeur
               S01:00008E94:  E2 FF FF CA
F00:1549       	
F00:1550       	ldr		R7,[R11],#4			; n° sprite source
               S01:00008E98:  04 70 9B E4
F00:1551       	add		R10,R10,#4			; on saute le n° sprite objet destination
               S01:00008E9C:  04 A0 8A E2
F00:1552       	str		R7,[R12],#4			; n° sprite table increment
               S01:00008EA0:  04 70 8C E4
F00:1553       		
F00:1554       	subs	R0,R0,#1
               S01:00008EA4:  01 00 50 E2
F00:1555       	bgt		boucle_preparation_transformation
               S01:00008EA8:  DC FF FF CA
F00:1556       ; sortie
F00:1557       	mov pc, r14
               S01:00008EAC:  0E F0 A0 E1
F00:1558       
F00:1559       
F00:1560       ;--------------	
F00:1561       ;	calcul progressif des X Y Z transformation
F00:1562       ;	source : pointeur_table_increments_pas_transformations : X source ,increment X, Y source, increment Y, Z source, incre
F00:1563       ;	dest : pointeur_buffer_coordonnees_objet_transformees
F00:1564       
F00:1565       
F00:1566       realisation_transformation:
F00:1567       
F00:1568       
F00:1569       		ldr		R12,pointeur_buffer_coordonnees_objet_transformees
               S01:00008EB0:  D0 C7 9F E5
F00:1570       		ldr		R11,pointeur_table_increments_pas_transformations
               S01:00008EB4:  E8 B7 9F E5
F00:1571       	
F00:1572       		ldr		R0,nb_points_objet_en_cours
               S01:00008EB8:  88 07 9F E5
F00:1573       
F00:1574       boucle_realisation_transformation:
F00:1575       		mov		R7,#3
               S01:00008EBC:  03 70 A0 E3
F00:1576       
F00:1577       boucle_realisation_transformation_1_valeur:
F00:1578       		ldr		R1,[R11]					; X * 2^15
               S01:00008EC0:  00 10 9B E5
F00:1579       		ldr		R2,[R11,#4]					; increment X * 2^15
               S01:00008EC4:  04 20 9B E5
F00:1580

               S01:00008EC8:  02 10 91 E0
F00:1582

               S01:00008ECC:  04 10 8B E4
F00:1584       		add		R11,R11,#4					; on passe l'increment
               S01:00008ED0:  04 B0 8B E2
F00:1585

               S01:00008ED4:  C1 17 A0 E1
F00:1587

               S01:00008ED8:  04 10 8C E4

               S01:00008EDC:  01 70 57 E2

               S01:00008EE0:  F6 FF FF CA

F00:2667       calc3D:
F00:2668       ; input : 
F00:2669       ;	- pointeur_points_objet_en_cours = pointeur vers les points 3D X,Y,Z
F00:2670       ;	- nb_points_objet_en_cours = nombre de points à calculer
F00:2671       ;	- pointeur_coordonnees_transformees = pointeur destination du resultats des calculs
F00:2672       
F00:2673       	str r14,save_R14
               S01:000097B0:  04 E3 8F E5
F00:2674       
F00:2675       	; calcul de la matrice de transformation
F00:2676       	;mov r12,#matrice
F00:2677       	ldr r11,pointeur_SINCOS
               S01:000097B4:  34 B3 9F E5
F00:2678       	
F00:2679       	
F00:2680       	ldr r1,angleX
               S01:000097B8:  D4 10 1F E5
F00:2681       	add r1,r11, r1, lsl #3
               S01:000097BC:  81 11 8B E0
F00:2682       	ldmia r1, {r2-r3}			
               S01:000097C0:  0C 00 91 E8
F00:2683       	; r2=SINX , r3=COSX
F00:2684       	
F00:2685       	ldr r1,angleY
               S01:000097C4:  DC 10 1F E5

F00:2689

               S01:000097D8:  C0 00 91 E8

F00:2694       	
F00:2695       	RSB r6,r6,#0
               S01:000097DC:  00 60 66 E2
F00:2696       	;mov r1,#0
F00:2697       	;sub r6,r1,r6
F00:2698       	;neg R6, ROTATION EN Z BUGGEE !!!
F00:2699       
F00:2700       	; r2-r7 utilisés
F00:2701       
F00:2702       	; calcul de CY*CZ
F00:2703       	muls r14, r5 , r7	; CY*CZ * 2^15*2^15
               S01:000097E0:  95 07 1E E0
F00:2704       	; # / 2^15

F00:2706       	mov r14,r14,asr #15	; / 32768
               S01:000097E4:  CE E7 A0 E1
F00:2707       	;str r1, [r12], #4	;r14
F00:2708

F00:2710       	muls r1,r5,r6	;r1=cy*sz
               S01:000097E8:  95 06 11 E0

               S01:000097EC:  C1 17 A0 E1

               S01:000097FC:  01 10 90 E0
F00:2716       	mov r0,#0
               S01:00009800:  00 00 A0 E3

F00:3146       bubblesort_XYZ:
F00:3147       ; X Y Z n0 sprite=> 4 * 4 = 16 octets
F00:3148       	ldr		R11,pointeur_coordonnees_projetees			; R11 = X
               S01:00009AF4:  C0 B4 1F E5
F00:3149       	add		R10,R11,#4							; R10 = Y
               S01:00009AF8:  04 A0 8B E2
F00:3150       	add		R0,R10,#4							; R0 = Z
               S01:00009AFC:  04 00 8A E2
F00:3151       	add		R12,R0,#4							; R12 = n° sprite
               S01:00009B00:  04 C0 80 E2
F00:3152       	ldr		R1,nb_points_objet_en_cours
               S01:00009B04:  C4 14 1F E5
F00:3153       
F00:3154       bsort_next:                     ;// Check for a sorted array
F00:3155           MOV     R2,#0               ;// R2 = Current Element Number
               S01:00009B08:  00 20 A0 E3
F00:3156           MOV     R6,#0               ;// R6 = Number of swaps
               S01:00009B0C:  00 60 A0 E3
F00:3157       bsort_loop:                     ;// Start loop
F00:3158           ADD     R3,R2,#1            ;// R3 = Next Element Number
               S01:00009B10:  01 30 82 E2
F00:3159           CMP     R3,R1               ;// Check for the end of the array
               S01:00009B14:  01 00 53 E1
F00:3160           BGE     bsort_check         ;// When we reach the end, check for changes
               S01:00009B18:  13 00 00 AA
F00:3161           LDR     R4,[R0,R2,LSL #4]   ;// R4 = Current Element Value
               S01:00009B1C:  02 42 90 E7
F00:3162           LDR     R5,[R0,R3,LSL #4]   ;// R5 = Next Element Value
               S01:00009B20:  03 52 90 E7
F00:3163           CMP     R5,R4               ;// Compare element values
               S01:00009B24:  04 00 55 E1
F00:3164       
F00:3165       ; Z
F00:3166           STRGT   R5,[R0,R2,LSL #4]   ;// If R4 > R5, store current value at next
               S01:00009B28:  02 52 80 C7
F00:3167           STRGT   R4,[R0,R3,LSL #4]   ;// If R4 > R5, Store next value at current
               S01:00009B2C:  03 42 80 C7
F00:3168       	
F00:3169       	LDRGT   R8,[R11,R2,LSL #4]	; X1
               S01:00009B30:  02 82 9B C7
F00:3170       	LDRGT   R9,[R11,R3,LSL #4]	; X2
               S01:00009B34:  03 92 9B C7
F00:3171       	STRGT   R9,[R11,R2,LSL #4]   ;// If R4 > R5, store current value at next
               S01:00009B38:  02 92 8B C7
F00:3172           STRGT   R8,[R11,R3,LSL #4]   ;// If R4 > R5, Store next value at current
               S01:00009B3C:  03 82 8B C7
F00:3173       
F00:3174       	LDRGT   R8,[R10,R2,LSL #4]	; Y1
               S01:00009B40:  02 82 9A C7
F00:3175       	LDRGT   R9,[R10,R3,LSL #4]	; Y2
               S01:00009B44:  03 92 9A C7
F00:3176       	STRGT   R9,[R10,R2,LSL #4]   ;// If R4 > R5, store current value at next
               S01:00009B48:  02 92 8A C7
F00:3177           STRGT   R8,[R10,R3,LSL #4]   ;// If R4 > R5, Store next value at current
               S01:00009B4C:  03 82 8A C7
F00:3178       	
F00:3179       	LDRGT   R8,[R12,R2,LSL #4]	; n° sprite 1
               S01:00009B50:  02 82 9C C7
F00:3180       	LDRGT   R9,[R12,R3,LSL #4]	; n° sprite 2
               S01:00009B54:  03 92 9C C7
F00:3181       	STRGT   R9,[R12,R2,LSL #4]   ;// If R4 > R5, store current value at next
               S01:00009B58:  02 92 8C C7
F00:3182           STRGT   R8,[R12,R3,LSL #4]   ;// If R4 > R5, Store next value at current
               S01:00009B5C:  03 82 8C C7
F00:3183       	
F00:3184       	
F00:3185           ADDGT   R6,R6,#1            ;// If R4 > R5, Increment swap counter
               S01:00009B60:  01 60 86 C2
F00:3186           MOV     R2,R3               ;// Advance to the next element
               S01:00009B64:  03 20 A0 E1
F00:3187           B       bsort_loop          ;// End loop
               S01:00009B68:  E8 FF FF EA
F00:3188       bsort_check:                    ;// Check for changes
F00:3189           CMP     R6,#0               ;// Were there changes this iteration?
               S01:00009B6C:  00 00 56 E3
F00:3190           SUBGT   R1,R1,#1            ;// Optimization: skip last value in next loop
               S01:00009B70:  01 10 41 C2
F00:3191           BGT     bsort_next          ;// If there were changes, do it again
               S01:00009B74:  E3 FF FF CA
F00:3192       bsort_done: 
F00:3193       
F00:3194       	mov		pc,lr
               S01:00009B78:  0E F0 A0 E1
F00:3195       
F00:3196       ;-------------------------------------------
F00:3197       copie_dans_buffer_calcul_final:
F00:3198       
F00:3199       ; encodage :
F00:3200       ; 9 bits pour X
F00:3201       ; 9 bits pour Y
F00:3202       ; 4 bits pour n° sprite
F00:3203       ; = 22 bits , reste 10 bits
F00:3204       
F00:3205       ; X << 13
F00:3206       ; Y << 4
F00:3207       ; X peut etre negatif
F00:3208       ; Y ne peut pas etre negatif
F00:3209       ; n° ne peut pas etre negatif
F00:3210       
F00:3211       
F00:3212       
F00:3213       	ldr		R0,nb_points_objet_en_cours_au_total
               S01:00009B7C:  38 05 1F E5
F00:3214       	
F00:3215       	ldr		R11,pointeur_coordonnees_projetees			; source
               S01:00009B80:  4C B5 1F E5
F00:3216       	ldr		R12,pointeur_actuel_buffer_en_cours_de_calcul		; destination
               S01:00009B84:  6C C5 1F E5
F00:3217       	
F00:3218       	ldr		r13,pointeur_table416
               S01:00009B88:  38 D4 9F E5
F00:3219       	
F00:3220       .boucle_copie_avec_reduction:
F00:3221       
F00:3222       
F00:3223       	ldmia	R11!,{R1-R4}
               S01:00009B8C:  1E 00 BB E8
F00:3224       
F00:3225       	
F00:3226       ;	ldr		R1,[R11],#4				; X projeté écran
F00:3227       ;	ldr		R2,[R11],#4				; Y projeté écran
F00:3228       ;	add		R11,R11,#4				; on saute le Z
F00:3229       ;	ldr		R4,[R11],#4				; n° sprite
F00:3230       
F00:3231       ; on calcule le position ecran
F00:3232       	ldr		R2,[r13,R2,asl #2]		; R2=Y * 416
               S01:00009B90:  02 21 9D E7
F00:3233       	adds	R2,R2,R1				; R1 = position mémoire écran : X + 416 * Y
               S01:00009B94:  01 20 92 E0
F00:3234       ; valeur maxi : 107 328 : 18 bits
F00:3235       ; il faut garder le bas du X pour choisir le bon décalage de  sprite
F00:3236       ;	mov		R2,R2,asl #2			; 2 bits pour position X 
F00:3237       
F00:3238       ;	and		R1,R1,#0b11				; on garde la position X sur 4
F00:3239       ;	adds	R2,R2,R1				; on ajoute à la position mémoire
F00:3240       	mov		R2,R2,asl #4			; + 4 bits pour le n° sprite 
               S01:00009B98:  02 22 A0 E1
F00:3241       	adds	R2,R2,R4				; + n° sprite		
               S01:00009B9C:  04 20 92 E0
F00:3242       	
F00:3243       	str		R2,[R12],#4
               S01:00009BA0:  04 20 8C E4
F00:3244       ; décodage
F00:3245       ; R1 = Y*416 +x << 4 + n° sprite
F00:3246       ; cible : R4=position, R5 = X n° décalage, R6 = n° sprite
F00:3247       ;	and		R6,R2,#0b1111
F00:3248       ;	mov		R2,R2,asr #4
F00:3249       ;	and		R5,R2,#0b11
F00:3250       ;	mov		R4,R2,asr #2
F00:3251       	
F00:3252       	
F00:3253       	
F00:3254       	subs	R0,R0,#1
               S01:00009BA4:  01 00 50 E2
F00:3255       	bgt		.boucle_copie_avec_reduction
               S01:00009BA8:  F7 FF FF CA
F00:3256       	
F00:3257       
F00:3258       	mov		pc,lr
               S01:00009BAC:  0E F0 A0 E1
F00:3259       
F00:3260       pointeur_pile_quick_sort:		.long	pile_quick_sort
               S01:00009BB0:  80 4D 02 00
F00:3261       
F00:3262       ; ------------------------------------------------------------
F00:3263       ;
F00:3264       ; QUICK SORT
F00:3265       ;
F00:3266       ; ------------------------------------------------------------
F00:3267       
F00:3268       
F00:3269       quick_sort:
F00:3270       
F00:3271       
F00:3272       ; X Y Z n0 sprite=> 4 * 4 = 16 octets
F00:3273       	ldr		R10,pointeur_coordonnees_projetees			; R10 = X
               S01:00009BB4:  80 A5 1F E5
F00:3274       	add		R11,R10,#4							; R11 = Y
               S01:00009BB8:  04 B0 8A E2
F00:3275       	add		R12,R11,#4							; R12	= Z
               S01:00009BBC:  04 C0 8B E2
F00:3276       	;add		R13,R12,#4							; R13 = n° sprite
F00:3277       	
F00:3278       	ldr		R1,nb_points_objet_en_cours
               S01:00009BC0:  80 15 1F E5
F00:3279       	
F00:3280       	ldr		R13,pointeur_pile_quick_sort
               S01:00009BC4:  1C D0 1F E5
F00:3281       
F00:3282       qsort:
F00:3283       ; push de tous les registres
F00:3284       	stmdb	R13!,{R0-R12,LR}
               S01:00009BC8:  FF 5F 2D E9
F00:3285       	
F00:3286       	MOV     R4,R12               ;// R4 = Array Location ( Z )
               S01:00009BCC:  0C 40 A0 E1
F00:3287       	MOV     R5,R1               ;// R5 - Array Size
               S01:00009BD0:  01 50 A0 E1
F00:3288       	CMP     R5,#1               ;// Check for an array of size <= 1
               S01:00009BD4:  01 00 55 E3
F00:3289           BLE     qsort_done          ;// If array size <= 1, return
               S01:00009BD8:  66 00 00 DA
F00:3290       	
F00:3291       	CMP     R5,#2               ;// Check for an array of size == 2
               S01:00009BDC:  02 00 55 E3
F00:3292       	BEQ     qsort_check         ;// If array size == 2, check values
               S01:00009BE0:  4F 00 00 0A
F00:3293       	
F00:3294       qsort_partition:
F00:3295       	mov		R2,R5,lsr #1		 ;// R2 = The middle element index , R1 / 2
               S01:00009BE4:  A5 20 A0 E1
F00:3296       	LDR     R6,[R4]             ;// R6 = Beginning of array value
               S01:00009BE8:  00 60 94 E5
F00:3297       	LDR     R7,[R4,R2,LSL #4]   ;// R7 = Middle of array value, *16 car X Y Z N°sprite = 16 octets
               S01:00009BEC:  02 72 94 E7
F00:3298       	SUB     R8,R5,#1             ;// R8 = Upper array bound index (len -1 1)
               S01:00009BF0:  01 80 45 E2
F00:3299       	LDR     R8,[R4,R8,LSL #4]   ;// R8 = End of the array value , *16 car X Y Z N°sprite = 16 octets
               S01:00009BF4:  08 82 94 E7
F00:3300       	
F00:3301       	CMP     R6,R7                ;// Sort the values
               S01:00009BF8:  07 00 56 E1
F00:3302       	MOVGT   R9,R6				 ;// echange R6 et R7
               S01:00009BFC:  06 90 A0 C1
F00:3303           MOVGT   R6,R7
               S01:00009C00:  07 60 A0 C1
F00:3304           MOVGT   R7,R9
               S01:00009C04:  09 70 A0 C1
F00:3305       	
F00:3306       	CMP     R7,R8
               S01:00009C08:  08 00 57 E1
F00:3307           MOVGT   R9,R7				 ;// echange R7 et R8
               S01:00009C0C:  07 90 A0 C1
F00:3308           MOVGT   R7,R8
               S01:00009C10:  08 70 A0 C1
F00:3309           MOVGT   R8,R9
               S01:00009C14:  09 80 A0 C1
F00:3310       	
F00:3311       	CMP     R6,R7
               S01:00009C18:  07 00 56 E1
F00:3312           MOVGT   R9,R6				 ;// echange R6 et R7 
               S01:00009C1C:  06 90 A0 C1
F00:3313           MOVGT   R6,R7
               S01:00009C20:  07 60 A0 C1
F00:3314           MOVGT   R7,R9
               S01:00009C24:  09 70 A0 C1
F00:3315       	
F00:3316       	MOV     R6,R7                ;// R6 = Pivot
               S01:00009C28:  07 60 A0 E1
F00:3317       	MOV     R7,#0                ;// R7 = Lower array bounds index
               S01:00009C2C:  00 70 A0 E3
F00:3318       	SUB     R8,R5,#1             ;// R8 = Upper array bounds index (len - 1)
               S01:00009C30:  01 80 45 E2
F00:3319       
F00:3320       qsort_loop:
F00:3321       	LDR     R0,[R4,R7,LSL #4]   ;// R0 = Lower value, Z, *16 car X Y Z N°sprite = 16 octets
               S01:00009C34:  07 02 94 E7
F00:3322       	LDR     R1,[R4,R8,LSL #4]   ;// R1 = Upper value , Z
               S01:00009C38:  08 12 94 E7
F00:3323       	CMP     R0,R6               ;// Compare lower value to pivot
               S01:00009C3C:  06 00 50 E1
F00:3324       	BEQ     qsort_loop_u        ;// If == pivot, do nothing
               S01:00009C40:  16 00 00 0A
F00:3325       	ADDLT   R7,R7,#1            ;// If < pivot, increment lower index
               S01:00009C44:  01 70 87 B2
F00:3326       	STRGE   R0,[R4,R8,LSL #4]  ; // If > pivot, swap values
               S01:00009C48:  08 02 84 A7
F00:3327       	STRGE   R1,[R4,R7,LSL #4]
               S01:00009C4C:  07 12 84 A7
F00:3328       ; X
F00:3329       	sub		R10,R4,#8			; position Z - 8 = X
               S01:00009C50:  08 A0 44 E2
F00:3330       	LDRGE	R0,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; X1
               S01:00009C54:  07 02 9A A7
F00:3331       	LDRGE	R1,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; X2
               S01:00009C58:  08 12 9A A7
F00:3332       	STRGE   R0,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; X1
               S01:00009C5C:  08 02 8A A7
F00:3333       	STRGE   R1,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; X2
               S01:00009C60:  07 12 8A A7
F00:3334       ; Y
F00:3335       	add		R10,R10,#4			; passe à position Y
               S01:00009C64:  04 A0 8A E2
F00:3336       	LDRGE	R0,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; Y1
               S01:00009C68:  07 02 9A A7
F00:3337       	LDRGE	R1,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; Y2
               S01:00009C6C:  08 12 9A A7
F00:3338       	STRGE   R0,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; Y1
               S01:00009C70:  08 02 8A A7
F00:3339       	STRGE   R1,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; Y2
               S01:00009C74:  07 12 8A A7
F00:3340       ; n° sprite
F00:3341       	add		R10,R10,#8			; passe à position n°sprite
               S01:00009C78:  08 A0 8A E2
F00:3342       	LDRGE	R0,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; n° 1
               S01:00009C7C:  07 02 9A A7
F00:3343       	LDRGE	R1,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; n°2
               S01:00009C80:  08 12 9A A7
F00:3344       	STRGE   R0,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; n°1
               S01:00009C84:  08 02 8A A7
F00:3345       	STRGE   R1,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; n°2
               S01:00009C88:  07 12 8A A7
F00:3346       
F00:3347       	SUBGE   R8,R8,#1            ; // if > pivot, decrement upper index
               S01:00009C8C:  01 80 48 A2
F00:3348       	CMP     R7,R8               ; // if indexes are the same, recurse
               S01:00009C90:  08 00 57 E1
F00:3349       	BEQ     qsort_recurse
               S01:00009C94:  18 00 00 0A
F00:3350       	LDR     R0,[R4,R7,LSL #4]  ; // R0 = Lower value
               S01:00009C98:  07 02 94 E7
F00:3351       	LDR     R1,[R4,R8,LSL #4]  ; // R1 = Upper value
               S01:00009C9C:  08 12 94 E7
F00:3352       
F00:3353       qsort_loop_u:
F00:3354       	CMP     R1,R6               ; // Compare upper value to pivot
               S01:00009CA0:  06 00 51 E1
F00:3355       	SUBGT   R8,R8,#1            ; // if > pivot, decrement upper index
               S01:00009CA4:  01 80 48 C2
F00:3356       	STRLE   R0,[R4,R8,LSL #4]  ; // If < pivot, swap values
               S01:00009CA8:  08 02 84 D7
F00:3357       	STRLE   R1,[R4,R7,LSL #4]
               S01:00009CAC:  07 12 84 D7
F00:3358       
F00:3359       ; X
F00:3360       	sub		R10,R4,#8			; position Z - 8 = X
               S01:00009CB0:  08 A0 44 E2
F00:3361       	LDRLE	R0,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; X1
               S01:00009CB4:  07 02 9A D7
F00:3362       	LDRLE	R1,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; X2
               S01:00009CB8:  08 12 9A D7
F00:3363       	STRLE   R0,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; X1
               S01:00009CBC:  08 02 8A D7
F00:3364       	STRLE   R1,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; X2
               S01:00009CC0:  07 12 8A D7
F00:3365       ; Y
F00:3366       	add		R10,R10,#4			; passe à position Y
               S01:00009CC4:  04 A0 8A E2
F00:3367       	LDRLE	R0,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; Y1
               S01:00009CC8:  07 02 9A D7
F00:3368       	LDRLE	R1,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; Y2
               S01:00009CCC:  08 12 9A D7
F00:3369       	STRLE   R0,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; Y1
               S01:00009CD0:  08 02 8A D7
F00:3370       	STRLE   R1,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; Y2
               S01:00009CD4:  07 12 8A D7
F00:3371       ; n° sprite
F00:3372       	add		R10,R10,#8			; passe à position n°sprite
               S01:00009CD8:  08 A0 8A E2
F00:3373       	LDRLE	R0,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; n° 1
               S01:00009CDC:  07 02 9A D7
F00:3374       	LDRLE	R1,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; n°2
               S01:00009CE0:  08 12 9A D7
F00:3375       	STRLE   R0,[R10,R8,LSL #4]	; n°1
               S01:00009CE4:  08 02 8A D7
F00:3376       	STRLE   R1,[R10,R7,LSL #4]	; n°2	
               S01:00009CE8:  07 12 8A D7
F00:3377       	
F00:3378       	
F00:3379       	ADDLE   R7,R7,#1			; // if < pivot, increment lower index
               S01:00009CEC:  01 70 87 D2
F00:3380       	CMP     R7,R8               ; // if indexes are the same, recurse
               S01:00009CF0:  08 00 57 E1
F00:3381       	BEQ     qsort_recurse
               S01:00009CF4:  00 00 00 0A
F00:3382       	B       qsort_loop          ; // Continue loop
               S01:00009CF8:  CD FF FF EA
F00:3383       	
F00:3384       qsort_recurse:
F00:3385       	MOV     R12,R4              ; // R0 = Location of the first bucket
               S01:00009CFC:  04 C0 A0 E1
F00:3386       	MOV     R1,R7               ; // R1 = Length of the first bucket
               S01:00009D00:  07 10 A0 E1
F00:3387       	BL      qsort               ; // Sort first bucket
               S01:00009D04:  AF FF FF EB
F00:3388       	ADD     R8,R8,#1            ; // R8 = 1 index past final index
               S01:00009D08:  01 80 88 E2
F00:3389       	CMP     R8,R5               ; // Compare final index to original length
               S01:00009D0C:  05 00 58 E1
F00:3390       	BGE     qsort_done          ; // If equal, return
               S01:00009D10:  18 00 00 AA
F00:3391       	ADD     R12,R4,R8,LSL #4    ; // R0 = Location of the second bucket , *16 car X Y Z N°sprite = 16 octets
               S01:00009D14:  08 C2 84 E0
F00:3392       	SUB     R1,R5,R8            ; // R1 = Length of the second bucket
               S01:00009D18:  08 10 45 E0
F00:3393       	BL      qsort               ; // Sort second bucket
               S01:00009D1C:  A9 FF FF EB
F00:3394       	B       qsort_done          ; // return
               S01:00009D20:  14 00 00 EA
F00:3395       	
F00:3396       qsort_check:
F00:3397       	LDR     R0,[R4]             ; // Load first value into R0
               S01:00009D24:  00 00 94 E5
F00:3398       	LDR     R1,[R4,#16]          ; // Load second value into R1
               S01:00009D28:  10 10 94 E5
F00:3399       	CMP     R0,R1               ; // Compare R0 and R1
               S01:00009D2C:  01 00 50 E1
F00:3400       	BLE     qsort_done          ; // If R1 <= R0, then we are done
               S01:00009D30:  10 00 00 DA
F00:3401       	
F00:3402       	STR     R1,[R4]             ; // Otherwise, swap values
               S01:00009D34:  00 10 84 E5
F00:3403       	STR     R0,[R4,#16]          ; //  *16 car X Y Z N°sprite = 16 octets
               S01:00009D38:  10 00 84 E5
F00:3404       ; X
F00:3405       	sub		R10,R4,#8			; position Z - 8 = X
               S01:00009D3C:  08 A0 44 E2
F00:3406       	LDR		R0,[R10]			; X1
               S01:00009D40:  00 00 9A E5
F00:3407       	LDR		R1,[R10,#16]		; X2
               S01:00009D44:  10 10 9A E5
F00:3408       	STR	    R1,[R10]	; X1
               S01:00009D48:  00 10 8A E5
F00:3409       	STR	    R0,[R10, #16]	; X2
               S01:00009D4C:  10 00 8A E5
F00:3410       ; Y
F00:3411       	add		R10,R10,#4			; passe à position Y
               S01:00009D50:  04 A0 8A E2
F00:3412       	LDR		R0,[R10]			; X1
               S01:00009D54:  00 00 9A E5
F00:3413       	LDR		R1,[R10,#16]		; X2
               S01:00009D58:  10 10 9A E5
F00:3414       	STR	    R1,[R10]	; X1
               S01:00009D5C:  00 10 8A E5
F00:3415       	STR	    R0,[R10, #16]	; X2
               S01:00009D60:  10 00 8A E5
F00:3416       ; n° sprite
F00:3417       	add		R10,R10,#8			; passe à position n°sprite
               S01:00009D64:  08 A0 8A E2
F00:3418       	LDR		R0,[R10]			; X1
               S01:00009D68:  00 00 9A E5
F00:3419       	LDR		R1,[R10,#16]		; X2
               S01:00009D6C:  10 10 9A E5
F00:3420       	STR	    R1,[R10]	; X1
               S01:00009D70:  00 10 8A E5
F00:3421       	STR	    R0,[R10, #16]	; X2
               S01:00009D74:  10 00 8A E5
F00:3422       
F00:3423       
F00:3424       
F00:3425       qsort_done:
F00:3426       
F00:3427       ; pop de tous les registres
F00:3428       	ldmia	R13!,{R0-R12,PC}
               S01:00009D78:  FF 9F BD E8
F00:3429       
F00:3430       ; ------------------------------------------------------------
F00:3431       ;
F00:3432       ; QUICK SORT 2eme version
F00:3433       ;
F00:3434       ; ------------------------------------------------------------
F00:3435       
F00:3436       
F00:3437       	
F00:3438       
F00:3439       quick_sort2:
F00:3440       ;  qsort:  @ Takes three parameters:
F00:3441       
F00:3442       ; R0 = pointeur vers le tableau de valeurs
F00:3443       ; R1 = 0
F00:3444       ; R2 = nb elements
F00:3445       
F00:3446       		ldr		sp,pointeur_pile_quick_sort
               S01:00009D7C:  D4 D1 1F E5
F00:3447       
F00:3448       		ldr		R0,pointeur_coordonnees_projetees
               S01:00009D80:  4C 07 1F E5
F00:3449       
F00:3450       
F00:3451       		add		R0,R0,#8			; pointe sur Z
               S01:00009D84:  08 00 80 E2
F00:3452       
F00:3453       		mov		R1,#0				; on commence à 0
               S01:00009D88:  00 10 A0 E3
F00:3454       		ldr		R2,nb_points_objet_en_cours_au_total
               S01:00009D8C:  48 27 1F E5
F00:3455       
F00:3456       ; dispos : R8 R9 R10 R11 R12 
F00:3457       
F00:3458       qsort2_qsort:
F00:3459       ;        @   a:     Pointer to base of array a to be sorted (arrives in r0)
F00:3460       ;        @   left:  First of the range of indexes to sort (arrives in r1)
F00:3461       ;        @   right: One past last of range of indexes to sort (arrives in r2)
F00:3462       ;        @ This function destroys: r1, r2, r3, r5, r7
F00:3463       
F00:3464               stmfd   sp!, {r4, r6, lr}     ; @ Save r4 and r6 for caller
               S01:00009D90:  50 40 2D E9
F00:3465               mov     r6, r2                ; @ r6 <- right
               S01:00009D94:  02 60 A0 E1
F00:3466       
F00:3467       qsort2_qsort_tailcall_entry:
F00:3468               sub     r7, r6, r1            ; @ If right - left <= 1 (already sorted),
               S01:00009D98:  01 70 46 E0
F00:3469               cmp     r7, #1
               S01:00009D9C:  01 00 57 E3
F00:3470               ldmlefd sp!, {r4, r6, pc}     ; @ Return, restoring r4 and r6
               S01:00009DA0:  50 80 BD D8
F00:3471       
F00:3472               ldr     r7, [r0, r1, asl #4]  ; @ r7 <- a[left], gets pivot element   	Z
               S01:00009DA4:  01 72 90 E7
F00:3473       		
F00:3474               add     r2, r1, #1            ; @ l <- left + 1
               S01:00009DA8:  01 20 81 E2
F00:3475               mov     r4, r6                ; @ r <- right
               S01:00009DAC:  06 40 A0 E1
F00:3476       		
F00:3477       		
F00:3478       qsort2_partition_loop:
F00:3479               ldr     r3, [r0, r2, asl #4]  ; @ r3 <- a[l]							Z
               S01:00009DB0:  02 32 90 E7
F00:3480       
F00:3481               cmp     r3, r7                ; @ If a[l] <= pivot_element,
               S01:00009DB4:  07 00 53 E1
F00:3482               addle   r2, r2, #1            ; @ ... increment l, and										SENS DU TRI
               S01:00009DB8:  01 20 82 D2
F00:3483               ble     qsort2_partition_test        ; @ ... continue to next iteration.					SENS DU TRI
               S01:00009DBC:  12 00 00 DA
F00:3484       
F00:3485               sub     r4, r4, #1            ; @ Otherwise, decrement r,
               S01:00009DC0:  01 40 44 E2
F00:3486               ldr     r5, [r0, r4, asl #4]  ; @ ... and swap a[l] and a[r].
               S01:00009DC4:  04 52 90 E7
F00:3487               str     r5, [r0, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009DC8:  02 52 80 E7
F00:3488               str     r3, [r0, r4, asl #4]
               S01:00009DCC:  04 32 80 E7
F00:3489       		
F00:3490       ; X
F00:3491       		sub		R12,R0,#8				; position en X
               S01:00009DD0:  08 C0 40 E2
F00:3492       		ldr     r3, [r12, r2, asl #4]		; X1
               S01:00009DD4:  02 32 9C E7
F00:3493       		ldr     r5, [r12, r4, asl #4]		; X2
               S01:00009DD8:  04 52 9C E7
F00:3494       		str     r5, [r12, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009DDC:  02 52 8C E7
F00:3495       		str     r3, [r12, r4, asl #4]
               S01:00009DE0:  04 32 8C E7
F00:3496       ; Y
F00:3497       		add		R12,R12,#4				; position en Y
               S01:00009DE4:  04 C0 8C E2
F00:3498       		ldr     r3, [r12, r2, asl #4]		; Y1
               S01:00009DE8:  02 32 9C E7
F00:3499       		ldr     r5, [r12, r4, asl #4]		; Y2
               S01:00009DEC:  04 52 9C E7
F00:3500       		str     r5, [r12, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009DF0:  02 52 8C E7
F00:3501       		str     r3, [r12, r4, asl #4]
               S01:00009DF4:  04 32 8C E7
F00:3502       ; n° sprite
F00:3503       		add		R12,R12,#8				; position en n° sprite
               S01:00009DF8:  08 C0 8C E2
F00:3504       		ldr     r3, [r12, r2, asl #4]		; 1
               S01:00009DFC:  02 32 9C E7
F00:3505       		ldr     r5, [r12, r4, asl #4]		; 2
               S01:00009E00:  04 52 9C E7
F00:3506       		str     r5, [r12, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009E04:  02 52 8C E7
F00:3507       		str     r3, [r12, r4, asl #4]
               S01:00009E08:  04 32 8C E7
F00:3508       		
F00:3509       		
F00:3510       
F00:3511       qsort2_partition_test:
F00:3512               cmp     r2, r4                ; @ If l < r,
               S01:00009E0C:  04 00 52 E1
F00:3513               blt     qsort2_partition_loop        ; @ ... continue iterating.
               S01:00009E10:  E6 FF FF BA
F00:3514       
F00:3515       qsort2_partition_finish:
F00:3516               sub     r2, r2, #1            ; @ Decrement l
               S01:00009E14:  01 20 42 E2
F00:3517               ldr     r3, [r0, r2, asl #4]  ; @ Swap a[l] and pivot
               S01:00009E18:  02 32 90 E7
F00:3518               str     r3, [r0, r1, asl #4]
               S01:00009E1C:  01 32 80 E7
F00:3519               str     r7, [r0, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009E20:  02 72 80 E7
F00:3520       
F00:3521       ; X
F00:3522       		sub		R12,R0,#8				; position en X		
               S01:00009E24:  08 C0 40 E2
F00:3523       		ldr     r3, [r12, r2, asl #4]		; X1
               S01:00009E28:  02 32 9C E7
F00:3524       		ldr     r5, [r12, r1, asl #4]		; X2
               S01:00009E2C:  01 52 9C E7
F00:3525       		str     r5, [r12, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009E30:  02 52 8C E7
F00:3526       		str     r3, [r12, r1, asl #4]
               S01:00009E34:  01 32 8C E7
F00:3527       ; Y
F00:3528       		add		R12,R12,#4				; position en Y
               S01:00009E38:  04 C0 8C E2
F00:3529       		ldr     r3, [r12, r2, asl #4]		; Y1
               S01:00009E3C:  02 32 9C E7
F00:3530       		ldr     r5, [r12, r1, asl #4]		; Y2
               S01:00009E40:  01 52 9C E7
F00:3531       		str     r5, [r12, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009E44:  02 52 8C E7
F00:3532       		str     r3, [r12, r1, asl #4]
               S01:00009E48:  01 32 8C E7
F00:3533       ; n° sprite
F00:3534       		add		R12,R12,#8				; position en n° sprite
               S01:00009E4C:  08 C0 8C E2
F00:3535       		ldr     r3, [r12, r2, asl #4]		; 1
               S01:00009E50:  02 32 9C E7
F00:3536       		ldr     r5, [r12, r1, asl #4]		; 2
               S01:00009E54:  01 52 9C E7
F00:3537       		str     r5, [r12, r2, asl #4]
               S01:00009E58:  02 52 8C E7
F00:3538       		str     r3, [r12, r1, asl #4]		
               S01:00009E5C:  01 32 8C E7
F00:3539       		
F00:3540       		
F00:3541               bl      qsort2_qsort                ;@ Call self recursively on left part,
               S01:00009E60:  CA FF FF EB
F00:3542                                             ;@  with args a (r0), left (r1), r (r2),
F00:3543                                             ;@  also preserves r4 and r6
F00:3544               mov     r1, r4
               S01:00009E64:  04 10 A0 E1
F00:3545               b       qsort2_qsort_tailcall_entry  ; @ Tail-call self on right part,
               S01:00009E68:  CA FF FF EA
F00:3546                                             ; @  with args a (r0), l (r1), right (r6)
F00:3547       
F00:3548       
F00:3549       
F00:3550       masque_decodage_X:			.long 0b11111111111111111110000000000000
               S01:00009E6C:  00 E0 FF FF

F00:3554       .include "palette.asm"
F07:0001       ; ============================================================================
F07:0002       ; Palette Utils
F07:0003       ; ============================================================================
F07:0004       
F07:0005       ; R3 = index
F07:0006       ; R4 = RGBx word   //   0BGR 0000
F07:0007       ; Uses R0,R1 
F07:0008       palette_set_colour:
F07:0009           adrl r1, palette_osword_block
               S01:00009E70:  01 1C 8F E2 04 10 81 E2
F07:0010           strb r3, [r1, #0]       ; logical colour
               S01:00009E78:  00 30 C1 E5
F07:0011       	
F07:0012           mov r0, #16
               S01:00009E7C:  10 00 A0 E3
F07:0013           strb r0, [r1, #1]       ; physical colour
               S01:00009E80:  01 00 C1 E5
F07:0014       	
F07:0015           and r0, r4, #0x0f0000		; R 
               S01:00009E84:  0F 08 04 E2
F07:0016       	mov r0, r0, lsr #16	
               S01:00009E88:  20 08 A0 E1
F07:0017           strb r0, [r1, #2]       ; red
               S01:00009E8C:  02 00 C1 E5
F07:0018           
F07:0019       	mov r0, r4, lsr #2
               S01:00009E90:  24 01 A0 E1
F07:0020       	and r0,r0,#0x0f
               S01:00009E94:  0F 00 00 E2
F07:0021           strb r0, [r1, #3]       ; green
               S01:00009E98:  03 00 C1 E5
F07:0022           
F07:0023       	mov r0, r4, lsr #24
               S01:00009E9C:  24 0C A0 E1
F07:0024       	and r0,r0,#0x0f
               S01:00009EA0:  0F 00 00 E2
F07:0025           strb r0, [r1, #4]       ; blue
               S01:00009EA4:  04 00 C1 E5
F07:0026           
F07:0027       	mov r0, #12
               S01:00009EA8:  0C 00 A0 E3
F07:0028           swi OS_Word
               S01:00009EAC:  07 00 00 EF
F07:0029       	
F07:0030           mov pc,lr
               S01:00009EB0:  0E F0 A0 E1
F07:0031       
F07:0032       ; R2 = palette block ptr
F07:0033       palette_set_block:
F07:0034       	str lr, [sp, #-4]!			; push lr on stack
               S01:00009EB4:  04 E0 2D E5
F07:0035           mov r3, #0
               S01:00009EB8:  00 30 A0 E3
F07:0036           .1:
F07:0037           ldr r4, [r2], #4            ; rgbx
               S01:00009EBC:  04 40 92 E4
F07:0038           bl palette_set_colour
               S01:00009EC0:  EA FF FF EB
F07:0039           add r3, r3, #1
               S01:00009EC4:  01 30 83 E2
F07:0040           cmp r3, #16
               S01:00009EC8:  10 00 53 E3
F07:0041           blt .1
               S01:00009ECC:  FA FF FF BA
F07:0042       	ldr pc, [sp], #4			; rts
               S01:00009ED0:  04 F0 9D E4
F07:0043       
F07:0044       ; R2 = palette block ptr
F07:0045       palette_make_greyscale:
F07:0046       	str lr, [sp, #-4]!			; push lr on stack
               S01:00009ED4:  04 E0 2D E5
F07:0047           adr r1, palette_interp_block
               S01:00009ED8:  A8 10 8F E2
F07:0048       
F07:0049           mov r3, #16
               S01:00009EDC:  10 30 A0 E3
F07:0050           .1:
F07:0051           ldr r4, [r2], #4            ; rgbx
               S01:00009EE0:  04 40 92 E4
F07:0052       
F07:0053           mov r5, r4, lsr #2          ; red * 0.25
               S01:00009EE4:  24 51 A0 E1
F07:0054           and r5, r5, #0xf0
               S01:00009EE8:  F0 50 05 E2
F07:0055           mov r6, r4, lsr #9          ; green * 0.5
               S01:00009EEC:  A4 64 A0 E1
F07:0056           and r6, r6, #0xf0
               S01:00009EF0:  F0 60 06 E2
F07:0057           mov r7, r4, lsr #18         ; blue * 0.25
               S01:00009EF4:  24 79 A0 E1
F07:0058           and r7, r7, #0xf0
               S01:00009EF8:  F0 70 07 E2
F07:0059           
F07:0060           add r0, r5, r6
               S01:00009EFC:  06 00 85 E0
F07:0061           add r0, r0, r7
               S01:00009F00:  07 00 80 E0
F07:0062           orr r0, r0, r0, lsl #8
               S01:00009F04:  00 04 80 E1
F07:0063           orr r0, r0, r0, lsl #8
               S01:00009F08:  00 04 80 E1
F07:0064       
F07:0065           str r0, [r1], #4
               S01:00009F0C:  04 00 81 E4
F07:0066           
F07:0067           subs r3, r3, #1
               S01:00009F10:  01 30 53 E2
F07:0068           bne .1
               S01:00009F14:  F1 FF FF 1A
F07:0069       	ldr pc, [sp], #4			; rts
               S01:00009F18:  04 F0 9D E4
F07:0070       
F07:0071       ; R0 = [0-16] interpolation
F07:0072       ; R2 = palette block ptr
F07:0073       palette_make_fade_to_black:
F07:0074       	str lr, [sp, #-4]!			; push lr on stack
               S01:00009F1C:  04 E0 2D E5
F07:0075           adr r1, palette_interp_block
               S01:00009F20:  60 10 8F E2
F07:0076       
F07:0077           mov r3, #16
               S01:00009F24:  10 30 A0 E3
F07:0078           .1:
F07:0079           ldr r4, [r2], #4            ; rgbx
               S01:00009F28:  04 40 92 E4
F07:0080       
F07:0081           mov r5, r4, lsr #4          ; rgbx / 16
               S01:00009F2C:  24 52 A0 E1
F07:0082           mul r6, r5, r0              ; r0 * rgbx / 16
               S01:00009F30:  95 00 06 E0
F07:0083       
F07:0084           str r6, [r1], #4
               S01:00009F34:  04 60 81 E4
F07:0085           
F07:0086           subs r3, r3, #1
               S01:00009F38:  01 30 53 E2
F07:0087           bne .1
               S01:00009F3C:  F9 FF FF 1A
F07:0088       	ldr pc, [sp], #4			; rts
               S01:00009F40:  04 F0 9D E4
F07:0089       
F07:0090       ; R0 = [0-16] interpolation
F07:0091       ; R2 = palette block ptr
F07:0092       palette_make_fade_to_white:
F07:0093       	str lr, [sp, #-4]!			; push lr on stack
               S01:00009F44:  04 E0 2D E5
F07:0094           adr r1, palette_interp_block
               S01:00009F48:  38 10 8F E2
F07:0095       
F07:0096           add r1, r1, #4              ; ignore 0
               S01:00009F4C:  04 10 81 E2
F07:0097           add r2, r2, #4              ; ignore 0
               S01:00009F50:  04 20 82 E2
F07:0098       
F07:0099           ldr r7, solid_white
               S01:00009F54:  28 70 9F E5
F07:0100           mov r3, #15
               S01:00009F58:  0F 30 A0 E3
F07:0101           .1:
F07:0102           ldr r4, [r2], #4            ; rgbx
               S01:00009F5C:  04 40 92 E4
F07:0103       
F07:0104           sub r5, r7, r4              ; white - rgbx
               S01:00009F60:  04 50 47 E0
F07:0105           mov r5, r5, lsr #4          ; (white - rgbx) / 16
               S01:00009F64:  25 52 A0 E1
F07:0106           mla r6, r5, r0, r4          ; rgbx + r0 * (white - rgbx) / 16
               S01:00009F68:  95 40 26 E0
F07:0107       
F07:0108           str r6, [r1], #4
               S01:00009F6C:  04 60 81 E4
F07:0109           
F07:0110           subs r3, r3, #1
               S01:00009F70:  01 30 53 E2
F07:0111           bne .1
               S01:00009F74:  F8 FF FF 1A
F07:0112       	ldr pc, [sp], #4			; rts
               S01:00009F78:  04 F0 9D E4
F07:0113

F07:0117           ; physical colour (16)
F07:0118           ; red

F07:0120           ; blue
